{"tid":467823,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"3個人做左3年既手機GAME終於要出啦","createTime":"2017-11-14T00:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T07:21:18.000Z","uid":37698,"like":8,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b61097ff173736241814a4badd9d8a232b0c3e60","tid":467823,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T00:40:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i6IIpdHnsGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di6IIpdHnsGs&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c42b35be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i6IIpdHnsGs</a><br />\n重新做的宣傳片<br />\n<br />\n事緣於4年幾前，玩左N年GAME既我，忽發奇想想做一隻自己既GAME。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時既我對手機遊戲製作一無所知，但我仍然搵左朋友即刻報讀左相關課程付諸行動。<br />\n時光倒流到2014年10月20日，就係依一日，我同2個朋友開始寫第一句代碼。<br />\n原本想用1年時間完成，因為無錢無人，結果一做做左3年，好多次想放棄都咬牙堅持落去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3年既時間話多唔多、話少唔少，但每日都需要費盡心血向困難、失敗、心灰戰鬥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻GAME戰鬥畫面有D似CC，但玩法完全唔同，唔係塔防GAME，係5V5回合制對戰的。<br />\n主要係講求組隊、技能、陣形、企位各種配合，戰鬥系統以簡單易上手為概念。<br />\n無可否認，我有參考過其他GAME好玩既元素，但我同時亦有加入好多自己既玩法。<br />\n要做一隻完全創新既GAME好難，就算大熱的LOL、爐石、魔塔都唔例外、融合左前人既玩法。<br />\n我唔知巿面有無一隻GAME同我依隻玩法一樣，至少我玩左幾百隻GAME未遇到過。<br />\n或者畫面、遊戲性、題材唔夠好、同大廠無得比，但係我地能力所能做到既最好既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好慶幸之前封測係高登開POST，雖然好多巴絲打未玩就屌到體無完膚搖搖慾墜<br />\n但亦都有好多巴絲打玩左俾左好多好好既意見我去改進。<br />\n例如：界面UI似小畫家，我改左簡潔清新既新界面(簡潔清新係某巴打對新界面既評價)<br />\n　　　音樂有Ｄ沉悶易訓，我又改用活潑既音樂<br />\n　　　戰鬥太慢，我加快左戰鬥(一場最多3分鐘)，同時加左一鍵「跳過」<br />\n　　　戰鬥模式太多容易亂，我將部份戰鬥模式先唔出住、將來更新再出<br />\n<br />\n或者睇依篇文只係花左你幾分鐘既插曲，但對我而言卻係燃燒左3年既努力同青春。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論遊戲成功唔成功，我已經完成左我既夢想，付諸行動做左一隻自己既GAME。<br />\n最後多謝你既閱讀，如果你有時間請先試玩一下，然後再俾我地意見，我地一定一定會接受同改善，感恩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：無錢宣傳，只可以係論壇、Facebook同叫朋友幫手宣傳<br />\n　　　網址域名係阿里雲申請的，論壇用既是Discuz。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>[遊戲下載及官網]　<a href=\"http://1m3k.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%2F&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=75b31ee9\" target=\"_blank\">http://1m3k.com/</a><br />\n[遊戲Facebook]　<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1m3kd%2F&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5c07c1a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/</a><br />\n開服時間：11月15日下晝5點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n備註：頭3000個註冊既acc會送300寶石，Facebook、論壇大量活動再送2000寶石<br />\n　　　開頭新手教送既銀卡，是旦揀就得，3張都差唔多勁</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7Id4NhL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7Id4NhL.png&h=b9843e45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc04a36c0c91ff4f69ce96f3816e33d597f6480c","tid":467823,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T00:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VmaE3dT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVmaE3dT.png&h=36435cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡潔清新的界面，一看就懂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cbrktCU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcbrktCU.png&h=c776cbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫師手繪、華麗魔幻畫風，不一樣的三國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S5BdXG3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FS5BdXG3.png&h=818167d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收集武將，初版多達100多名武將登場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vx1cmV2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVx1cmV2.png&h=7ca7a13a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戰鬥系統簡單易上手，5V5對戰，手動發動技能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CerFQMa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCerFQMa.png&h=5a583935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設有組隊COST限制，真正公平的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wku2TnU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fwku2TnU.png&h=74751e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n注重陣形、站位、技能等配搭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NpEDwxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNpEDwxV.jpg&h=a8279e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指名對戰，能夠和好友及不同的對手對戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2IkbQBZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2IkbQBZ.jpg&h=d98b3ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拜訪好友、贈送禮物給好友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gYfqDAZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgYfqDAZ.png&h=e208e4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開放了交易所，玩家間能自由買賣武將！"},{"pid":"bceea6c1e763e052816ae4c1d193aea32673fe25","tid":467823,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"30f68d410e04f46e3fa5ce51b38b60a251875c5c","tid":467823,"uid":37698,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T00:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/MmsK1j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FMmsK1j.png&h=d682d9cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n簡潔清新的界面，一看就懂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5A4TF7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5A4TF7.png&h=58797e5e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n畫師手繪、華麗魔幻畫風，不一樣的三國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/qp1Sv3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fqp1Sv3.png&h=9331861b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n收集武將，初版多達100多名武將登場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/MmbG13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FMmbG13.png&h=e9afcaa4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n戰鬥系統簡單易上手，5V5對戰，手動發動技能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/HS6fDb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FHS6fDb.png&h=42d82f27&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n設有組隊COST限制，真正公平的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/4nPxYX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F4nPxYX.png&h=2094da01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n注重陣形、站位、技能等配搭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/FZX4jd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FFZX4jd.jpg&h=6b15aae5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n指名對戰，能夠和好友及不同的對手對戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/1c0Gso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F1c0Gso.jpg&h=8f727d36&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n拜訪好友、贈送禮物給好友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/yQ8WZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FyQ8WZM.png&h=e51fae0b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n開放了交易所，玩家間能自由買賣武將！"},{"pid":"9cfc805ab5484aa30c2a6abb1f2760131cbea036","tid":467823,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"[戰鬥模式介紹] <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/wMPWlm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FwMPWlm.png&h=58a1aeb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲關卡主線 <br />\n每個小關卡分3個難度，設有不同的過關條件。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/vpiVXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FvpiVXa.jpg&h=eabbd2f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲排名對戰 <br />\n除了能挑戰排名，也能和好友及指名的對手對戰。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/SAanwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FSAanwE.jpg&h=2af55228&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲連環戰場 <br />\n挑戰極限的模式，設有排名榜。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/MEO8be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FMEO8be.jpg&h=18d3f48b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲銅雀台 <br />\n遊戲活動，只在每日10.00、15.00、20.00三個時段開放。(打裝專用) <br />\n<br />\n▲其他 <br />\n探險：稍後開放，快速消耗米糧的方式，有時會遇見賊軍，擊殺有豐富獎勵。 <br />\n主題競技場：稍後開放，遊戲活動，每星期一次，和玩家對戰，每次要求的主題不同。"},{"pid":"4fecc4b91266fc8230c42be464937f0fb155b9f2","tid":467823,"uid":121087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:26:03.000Z","msg":"係邊度學寫game?"},{"pid":"8d463d4d2c298082b6d48eec0735fa4e62cb429f","tid":467823,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"支持~ APK 有未?"},{"pid":"154d5e4c87cb5fe64e257847cf23ff10b1b66c52","tid":467823,"uid":142945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"iOS ？"},{"pid":"a4e4cc93f6df82807488a4a0508fc69b6feedf88","tid":467823,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名等玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5aa15cab47305d49d433c32807bd617ba9a2689","tid":467823,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"4fec9bcaa43bbe51fc2b3896a741230610ce2c92","tid":467823,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"公仔太q接受唔到"},{"pid":"3569241016b5acbd83f764ed0b5b1b8ef2298f0d","tid":467823,"uid":31884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"IOS表示期待"},{"pid":"164e0c9c5574fbbbb41ebaffbe73e9e67b6d90da","tid":467823,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"粉紅色頭條女個樣咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc306f6137fb84c0ac1ba56ec143bbc211d1635","tid":467823,"uid":44042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:10:19.000Z","msg":"呂布渣劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c355c2c49abd0afb95e3af9689765ffc54fee5","tid":467823,"uid":43042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"介面抄三國萌萌打?"},{"pid":"d61be5f0d7d73c0abed2d2f7ec0918ad1314952c","tid":467823,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T00:20:54.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意d畫"},{"pid":"211ad7fb4f3a7ad06cc3f91b2372c8c594875719","tid":467823,"uid":47464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"金卡1%仲低過出面普遍既遊戲喎............. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb89475137c4873bbf54ad72e4b4dd5c7925c6a5","tid":467823,"uid":11260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:19:03.000Z","msg":"一堆中文突然有個cost字小弟覺得有少少奇怪"},{"pid":"3b4581a2462682cfb03cff38ba07f81ed8222d3d","tid":467823,"uid":13421,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"好心自己整game就創新少少，整埋d市場已經有大把既game有咩意思？"},{"pid":"74efdfefc86fea5de080a6fa68148bdfe86d726a","tid":467823,"uid":27143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"點都叫一番心血 支持"},{"pid":"da81bd7cb8551b349286282dda604043e2333549","tid":467823,"uid":11260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心自己整game就創新少少，整埋d市場已經有大把既game有咩意思？</blockquote><br />\nAgger. 三國主題遊戲咁多年已經好多好多，市場已經飽和。畫面黨又唔會試，就算玩法創新都要吸引到人試先"},{"pid":"b70f9e464b8904d7390e2d1b6df5af3b7ec7981d","tid":467823,"uid":89418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"想問呢種玩法有幾創新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e9fd37a9cd88eb34e87b4f11dfe3589fbebd04","tid":467823,"uid":65774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"成隻支那game咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ac1d5cf5ebe55bbc9040e0d1d9b2c039124964","tid":467823,"uid":125258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"On9學人整課金game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}